00:32:19.660 --> 00:32:23.090
It's the single best
paper in the field.

00:32:23.090 --> 00:32:26.100
She's also done thoughtful
work on lobbying

00:32:26.100 --> 00:32:28.980
and on federal
Indian law, and she

00:32:28.980 --> 00:32:33.250
helped immensely in the
creation of the framework

00:32:33.250 --> 00:32:36.220
for this conference.

00:32:36.220 --> 00:32:38.500
Having gotten to know her
over the last couple years

00:32:38.500 --> 00:32:42.340
has been a privilege
and pleasure.

00:32:42.340 --> 00:32:45.500
As I am a student, a
very amateur student

00:32:45.500 --> 00:32:49.240
of Native American politics and
Native American petitioning,

00:32:49.240 --> 00:32:52.100
it is with frequency but
with patience and kindness

00:32:52.100 --> 00:32:56.020
that Maggie often corrects
me on my historical facts

00:32:56.020 --> 00:32:59.030
and cultural
misapprehensions, and I

00:32:59.030 --> 00:33:01.760
have to admit they are many.

00:33:01.760 --> 00:33:03.645
But I am indeed
honored to call her

00:33:03.645 --> 00:33:06.990
